<h1>Button</h1>
<p>Second most common call-to-action element. Used for triggering actions other than navigation.</p>
<h2>Demo</h2>
<code-sample>
<button ord="primary">Primary</button>
<button ord="secondary">Secondary</button>
<button ord="tertiary">Tertiary</button>
<a is="button" ord="primary" href="/">Link</a>
</code-sample>
