<h2>Guidelines</h2>
<h3>Button or link?</h3>
<p>If the action is to navigate, use a regular <a href="link">link</a>, but if that link also needs to look like a button then use the <code>is=button</code> attribute. If the action is not navigation, then use <code>button</code>.</p>
